544
01:51:05,734 --> 01:51:08,169
How could it not exist?
It's an historic monument.

545
01:51:08,170 --> 01:51:09,771
Of course.

546
01:51:09,772 --> 01:51:13,408
Have you heard
of Professor Dominic Matei?

547
01:51:13,409 --> 01:51:15,009
You know,
I was born here.

548
01:51:15,010 --> 01:51:17,812
Then you know that
he frequented Café Select

549
01:51:17,813 --> 01:51:21,416
