professor here in Piatra Neamt.

550
01:51:21,417 --> 01:51:22,417
That's right.

551
01:51:22,418 --> 01:51:24,486
Here's your key.

552
01:51:24,487 --> 01:51:25,487
[BELL DINGS]

553
01:51:25,488 --> 01:51:27,188
Nineteen?

554
01:51:27,189 --> 01:51:28,289
The second floor.

555
01:51:28,290 --> 01:51:29,424
All right.

556
01:51:29,425 --> 01:51:31,226
[GROANS]

557
01:51:31,227 --> 01:51:32,894
Welcome home.

558
01:51:32,895 --> 01:51:33,895
[SIGHS]

559
01:51:40,102 --> 01:51:41,736
Café Select.

560
01:51:45,841 --> 01:51:46,808
[SIGHS]

561
