<i>GIRL:</i>
<i>Maman.</i>

568
01:52:23,479 --> 01:52:25,447
<i>Maman.</i>

569
01:52:25,448 --> 01:52:26,448
[CAMERA CLICKS]

570
01:52:26,449 --> 01:52:27,182
<i>BOY:</i>
<i>Maman.</i>

571
01:52:28,350 --> 01:52:30,985
<i>Maman.</i>

572
01:52:30,986 --> 01:52:33,822
[BOY SPEAKS IN FRENCH]

573
01:52:33,823 --> 01:52:34,956
[VERONICA SPEAKS IN FRENCH]

574
01:52:37,193 --> 01:52:37,992
[SIGHS]

575
01:52:43,799 --> 01:52:44,966
[SNIFFLES]

576
01:52:56,846 --> 01:52:59,280
DOMINIC: "Good and
evil lose their meaning,

577
01:52:59,281 --> 01:53:01,049
"and in the absolute

578
01:53:01,050 --> 01:53:04,886
being coincides
with nonbeing."

579
01:53:04,887 --> 01:53:06,254
Yes, but what no one dares
to say

580
01:53:06,255 --> 01:53:08,356
is that in the horizon
of these philosophies,

581
01:53:08,357 --> 01:53:09,457
atomic wars must be,

582
01:53:09,458 --> 01:53:10,959
if not justified,
at least accepted.

583
01:53:10,960 --> 01:53:12,660
No, I reject that.

584
01:53:12,661 --> 01:53:15,163
True meaning of nuclear
catastrophe can only be this:

585
01:53:15,164 --> 01:53:17,332
The mutation
of the human species,

586
01:53:17,333 --> 01:53:18,800
and the arrival
of the new man.

587
01:53:18,801 --> 01:53:19,934
Yes, but atomic wars

588
01:53:19,935 --> 01:53:23,271
will destroy populations,
civilizations.

589
01:53:23,272 --> 01:53:25,874
That is the price to be paid.

590
01:53:25,875 --> 01:53:28,009
How can you even say that?

591
01:53:28,010 --> 01:53:30,678
The resulting electromagnetic
pulse will create

592
01:53:30,679 --> 01:53:32,914
an unlimited potential
for post-historic man.

593
01:53:32,915 --> 01:53:34,682
Yes, but it could go
the other way

594
01:53:34,683 --> 01:53:36,551
and provoke a regression
in the species.

595
01:53:36,552 --> 01:53:38,787
All that matters is knowledge

596
01:53:38,788 --> 01:53:40,722
and the perfection
of the human being.

597
01:53:40,723 --> 01:53:44,292
So you're saying that the end
justifies the means?

598
01:53:44,293 --> 01:53:46,995
There is no other way.

599
01:53:46,996 --> 01:53:49,297
Just as there was no other way
for Veronica, just aging

600
01:53:49,298 --> 01:53:50,832
and suffering and then death.

601
01:53:50,833 --> 01:53:52,867
There was no other way.

602
01:53:52,868 --> 01:53:54,969
That's why you've never
finished your book,

603
01:53:54,970 --> 01:53:56,971
why you'll always be a failure.

604
01:53:56,972 --> 01:53:57,839
No.

605
01:54:01,243 --> 01:54:03,278
THE DOUBLE:
Dominic, what have you done?

606
01:54:03,279 --> 01:54:04,813
[GASPING]

607
01:54:04,814 --> 01:54:05,914
Oh, Dominic.

608
01:54:05,915 --> 01:54:08,917
Save me.
Save me, Dominic.

609
01:54:11,287 --> 01:54:13,021
Dominic, what have you done?

610
01:54:13,022 --> 01:54:14,355
What have you done?

611
01:54:14,356 --> 01:54:16,357
[PANTING]

612
01:54:16,358 --> 01:54:18,326
[THE DOUBLE SPEAKING
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

613
01:54:35,311 --> 01:54:36,244
[SIGHS]

614
01:54:44,019 --> 01:54:45,453
[DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE]

615
01:54:50,259 --> 01:54:51,359
[SNIFFS]

616
01:54:56,265 --> 01:54:57,398
[CHUCKLES]

617
01:54:59,435 --> 01:55:01,536
[#]

