01:55:05,274 --> 01:55:06,007
[EXHALES]

619
01:55:48,651 --> 01:55:50,685
And the third rose?

620
01:55:52,655 --> 01:55:53,755
[SIGHS]

621
01:55:56,525 --> 01:55:59,127
[WHISPERS] Where shall
I put the third rose?

622
01:55:59,128 --> 01:56:00,228
[SNIFFLES]

623
01:56:02,665 --> 01:56:04,732
[WHISPERS]
Oh, where shall I put it?

